{"tid":198640,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[幫手解夢] 琴晚發咗個夢中夢","createTime":"2017-04-12T16:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T20:38:19.000Z","uid":45316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0cdb44e389bae40801ccb037bb5002c44a92899e","tid":198640,"uid":45316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:03:56.000Z","msg":"具體內容唔太記得<br />\n淨係記得自己係夢入面瞓覺發夢<br />\n夢中醒咗嘅時候又變返瞓之前嘅時間<br />\n連續loop咗4次先醒到 好似不斷重複發生過嘅夢咁<br />\n瞓醒嗰陣好淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人試過同樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"3956733346ad091ec2ed56201797be01a689fa4d","tid":198640,"uid":45316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:06:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"26d05ff94ee6f2d0164b4c6fe3c005ddba0df294","tid":198640,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:06:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24e65fde9f5f3fa3b19bdabd1d853de1959cd956","tid":198640,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:09:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"443d0831d497d4ac337916ae697f6f1f2dbae3bb","tid":198640,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:09:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c093aa362f879467763217a56d41ac7e14bd849","tid":198640,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:09:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd28ea84a52fea3e65e5a898ff7def0c899a19ec","tid":198640,"uid":45316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:16:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過喺個夢度出唔番黎<br />\n我試過<br />\n第一次發生喺差唔多一年前<br />\n一開始嘅視覺係自己平時訓醒但仲訓喺張床所見到嘅野<br />\n我以為自己醒左<br />\n但我發現自己點郁都冇知覺，宜自己睇到嘅野都冇變<br />\n我開始懷疑自己喺個夢到<br />\n但係我始終都係出唔番去現實<br />\n我好驚<br />\n好驚會一直困喺入面<br />\n同埋喺個夢度<br />\n我想訓覺但訓唔到<br />\n又攰又驚<br />\n最後唔記得點樣先醒番<br />\n成個過程可能只係幾分鐘<br />\n但對於我來講已經好長<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二次<br />\n發生喺第一次嘅一個星期後<br />\n果次係最恐怖....</blockquote><br />\n我一醒就睇時間 好驚啲時間又重複loop過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b64816f41780664c81d42ad827a4b1d014f714","tid":198640,"uid":5271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:47:58.000Z","msg":"試過<br />\n最後要大力控制自己手腳<br />\n先出返嚟<br />\n唔可以齋諗郁，要手動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca68205fcc1713d47c8d7021fbf3fac7b3b2d0c","tid":198640,"uid":44068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T20:38:19.000Z","msg":"身體太累<br />\n但頭腦清醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好話打機冇用 打鋪機可以令個腦累d <br />\n或者玩下數獨個d"}]}